Mapo Tofu
r2\r2.jpg
r2\r2.jpg
Chinese
Medium
30 m	20 m
Mapo tofu is one of the top ten famous Chinese dishes and enjoys a high popularity among not only Chinese people but also many western countries.
7
r2\steps\step1.jpg		Heat cooking oil and Sichuan oil in wok or pan, put chili bean paste, spicy black bean, sauté it.
r2\steps\step2.jpg		Add ginger, garlic, chili powder and sauté for a while.
r2\steps\step3.jpg		Add dark soy and water.
r2\steps\step4.jpg		Put silken tofu, leeks, spring onion, and add sugar, let it boil for 2 minutes.
r2\steps\step5.jpg		Meanwhile take a stainless steel bowl put potato starch and water to prepare thickening starch.
r2\steps\step6.jpg		Adjust the thickening with potato starch and add it.
r2\steps\r2.jpg	Congratulations! You are the chef.	b
1 tsp	chilli bean paste	beanPaste.jpg
300 gms	diced silken tofu	tofu.jpg
1/2 tsp	sichuan oil	sichuanOil.jpg
1 tsp	spicy black bean	spicyBlackBean.jpg
1/2 tsp	dark soy	darkSoy.jpg
1/2 tsp	red chili powder	redChiliPowder.jpg
1/2 tsp	sugar	sugar.jpg
1 tsp	spring onions, chopped	onions.jpg
1 tsp	ginger, chopped	ginger.jpg
1 tsp	garlic, chopped	garlic.jpg